=== rex.io - A cloud deployment cli 

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 This project is work in progress. It may change unexpectedly.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Use ini files to deploy services on all the cloud providers supported by (R)?ex.

$> cat cloud.ini 
[cloud]
service = Jiffybox
access_key = m7aPye6M0Xx7kW9j9JLdSLKGfv95md5x

[systemauth]
user = root
password = blahblah1234

[www]
type = static
root = static
instances = 1

[backend]
type = php
root = backend
instances = 1
;dns = backend.rexify.org
